title: Internet roasts Ciara and Russell Wilson for weird pregnancy photo (13 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
So Ciara just posted some maternity photos to her social media accounts of her, her son, and her husband Russell Wilson. The photo might be the weirdest pregnancy photo we’ve ever seen–I mean you can’t even see the face of Wilson and all the limbs involved look like a Chutes and Ladders board game. 
And of course, the internet had to respond. 2
